'''''Pride of Selonia''''' was a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] of the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]].

In [[9 ABY/Legends|9 ABY]], ''Pride of Selonia'' was escorting a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] supply convoy en route to [[Liinade III]] when the fleet was pulled from [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] into the [[M2934738 system/Legends|M2934738 system]] by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Immobilizer 418 Interdictor-class Heavy Cruiser|Interdictor cruiser]] ''[[Binder]]''. In the subsequent battle, ''Pride of Selonia'' was the first ship of the convoy to be destroyed by [[Reckoning (Imperial II-class)|''Reckoning'']]{{'s}} barrages.

